        <content type="html"><![CDATA[<h1 id="First-Blog-🎉🎉🎉">First Blog 🎉🎉🎉</h1><h2 id="2022-年-4-月-8-日-星期五">2022 年 4 月 8 日 星期五</h2><div class="note success flat"><p>早就想过建个 Blog ，今天终于实现了</p></div><ul><li><strong>刚好多用用</strong> <wavy>Markdown</wavy></li></ul><figure class="highlight plaintext"><table><tr><td class="gutter"><pre><span class="line">1</span><br></pre></td><td class="code"><pre><span class="line">用熟了应该会很方便</span><br></pre></td></tr></table></figure><ul><li><emp>本文亦在测试</emp>&nbsp;Tag Plugins Plus 写法</li></ul><h2 id="Future">Future</h2><div class='checkbox yellow checked'><input type="radio" checked="checked"/>            <p>能有时间打理打理门面</p>            </div><div class='checkbox green checked'><input type="radio" checked="checked"/>            <p>能写些有意义的文章</p>            </div><div class='checkbox cyan'><input type="radio" />            <p>能寻得一份宁静</p>            </div><blockquote><div class='checkbox red checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>记录生活</p>            </div><div class='checkbox yellow checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>分享学习</p>            </div> <div class='checkbox green checked'><input type="checkbox" checked="checked"/>            <p>陶冶情操</p>            </div><div class='checkbox blue'><input type="checkbox" />            <p>喵喵喵喵</p>            </div></blockquote><hr><img src="https://res.cloudinary.com/misaka/image/upload/v1651347174/blog_img/IMG_0345_apdset.jpg" width="90%"><p><strong>Image Source :</strong> <a href="https://www.deviantart.com/adiim/art/Saekano-Wallpaper-718212215">Adiim</a></p><p><strong>感谢 <a href="https://t.me/Likescatbot">赖小瑜</a></strong></p>]]></content>
      
      
